  EffectDiscription_ENG: "[On Play] \uFF1CDe-Digivolve 1\uFF1E all of your opponent's
    Digimon. Then, delete 1 of your opponent's Digimon with a play cost of 5 or less.
    If no Digimon is deleted by this effect, none of your opponent's unsuspended
    Digimon can digivolve until the end of your opponent's turn.[Opponent's Turn]
    While you have a Tamer in play, this Digimon gains \uFF1CBlocker\uFF1E and \uFF1CReboot\uFF1E."
